{"tid":1818602,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"汰弱留強 戰鬥民族父母讓兒睡陽台 7月大男嬰-7℃活活凍死","createTime":"2020-01-10T04:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T07:13:19.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"232fe5026c138fff17ba543ca0ad09876449efbe","tid":1818602,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"北歐和俄羅斯有讓嬰兒在戶外小睡的習慣，認為這樣能提高新生兒免疫力，減少感冒，不過前提是嬰兒有做好充足保暖，加上家長隨時注意。<br />\n <br />\n俄羅斯喀巴羅普斯克（Khabarovsk）一對父母把7個月大的兒子放在嬰兒車內，讓他睡在陽台，以為這樣可讓他「睡在新鮮空氣中」，但男嬰卻在攝氏零下7度的低溫中凍死。經當局初步勘驗，男嬰死於失溫，相關單位已展開調查。"},{"pid":"faa87bcbd92d243a7b72d377959c9366995ab98d","tid":1818602,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"700dd5e92af359315b0ef99d2b07cb847af9e667","tid":1818602,"uid":188176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:58:41.000Z","msg":"u can't survive winter 呢樣野佢地真係好重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c038a70619e87d57430bc606ab9d69a15824e304","tid":1818602,"uid":283438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:59:43.000Z","msg":"達爾文獎"},{"pid":"a45a2310b69edd4e1b4679da16e62a06a97f4575","tid":1818602,"uid":15954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:01:52.000Z","msg":"凍死德軍同拿破倫既冬將軍"},{"pid":"a899525e2798c0a2ee7b8b683938f221c4aa1311","tid":1818602,"uid":210669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"f8d66f38642ee840d9a56f69ff93ac0d90c64801","tid":1818602,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:03:22.000Z","msg":"睇得多龍珠?"},{"pid":"c9c6d9651210202c4ffd9d0f8418f2968097423e","tid":1818602,"